  <scopecontent id="aspace_7613935955c27dd5b656afbb8e87e9b6">
    <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
<p>This collection contains correspondence (mostly that of Jeff Cohen), internal documents, reports and studies, editorial material pertaining to <emph render="italic">Extra!</emph>, back issues (1992) of <title render="italic">Counterspin: A Memo on Campaign Coverage from FAIR</title>, published and unpublished writings by Jeff Cohen and others, a file on FAIR's Los Angeles chapter, and another on related organizations.</p>  </scopecontent>
